<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٢٩٧ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5093">أَبُو نُعَيْمٍ، </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2472">سُفْيَانُ. </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5178">قَبِيصَةُ، </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2472">سُفْيَانُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6869">يَحْيَى بْنِ أَبِي إِسْحَاقَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسٍ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«أَقَمْنَا مَعَ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> عَشْرًا نَقْصُرُ الصَّلَاةَ»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>